{"id":363206,"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/37/98/379815.jpg","floor":"#1","group":"靠谱人生茶话会","groupHref":"/group/boring","groupThumb":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/icon/m/000/00/03/364.jpg","message":"早闻班友卧虎藏龙，今日第一次发帖，请教各位一本画集的事<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/49.gif\" smileid=\"88\" alt=\"(bgm72)\"><br><br><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">超大图像警告</span>（图床：sm.ms）<br><br>5月29日，我拉着一个苦力和我一起去一家书店最深处的堆灰轻小说里面翻找<br>翻了2个小时，在挑选买哪本的时候，我注意到放画集的柜上竟然有本日文标题的画集<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/86.gif\" smileid=\"125\" alt=\"(bgm109)\"><br>（情景再现）<br><a href=\"https://sm.ms/image/MJnHlmf5vsEL6tW\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\"><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/06/07/MJnHlmf5vsEL6tW.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt></a><br><br>我觉得很奇怪，然后我抽出来一看，哦吼，居然是<br><a href=\"https://sm.ms/image/X8WiuM3D6vOIC4N\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\"><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/06/07/X8WiuM3D6vOIC4N.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt></a><br><a href=\"https://sm.ms/image/84Lf56p2YlQeiWn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\"><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/06/07/84Lf56p2YlQeiWn.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt></a><br>我也没多想，没仔细看就买了下来<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/59.gif\" smileid=\"98\" alt=\"(bgm82)\"><br><br>等我拿回家，打开版权页一看<br><a href=\"https://sm.ms/image/R5tjKOnUe29gIX7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\"><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/06/07/R5tjKOnUe29gIX7.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt></a><br>我整个人都蒙了，这难道是日文原版吗？<br><br>返回去一看，背面的ISBN是日文原版的，出版商也标的是Kadokawa<br>唯一有毛病的地方就是定价居然是中文的，还是RMB单位，就离谱！<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/37.gif\" smileid=\"76\" alt=\"(bgm60)\"><br><a href=\"https://sm.ms/image/EDsdzmRFTNKiZua\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\"><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/06/07/EDsdzmRFTNKiZua.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt></a><br><a href=\"https://sm.ms/image/R9lSfUDPZmbi6Xa\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\"><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/06/07/R9lSfUDPZmbi6Xa.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt></a><br><br>我赶紧打开病娇娘查了一手日文原版的扫描件，对比了一下内容，发现一页不少<br>唯一有区别的是封面标题文字是金色，而这本是红色（病娇娘上的版权页是2016年4月再版，而这本的版权页是2016年3月初版，估计是这个问题——）<br><br>由于家里没有扫描仪，只能用单反粗暴拍了几张来展示它的印刷质量。<br><a href=\"https://sm.ms/image/PN2KFpjycd74hAn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\"><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/06/07/PN2KFpjycd74hAn.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt></a><br><a href=\"https://sm.ms/image/TGKLvFf7UJrYln5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\"><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/06/07/TGKLvFf7UJrYln5.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt></a><br><a href=\"https://sm.ms/image/CWXbYAyIsnU76P4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\"><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/06/07/CWXbYAyIsnU76P4.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt></a><br>个人以为印刷有点模糊，但打开病娇娘的扫描图，发现其实也是差不多模糊<br><br>我也不是没买过盗版轻小说，大概知道盗版是怎样的。但是这本画集让我很迷糊，它的印刷应该不是扫描扫出来的那种图像，尤其是外封的反光材质，做得这么精细很离谱。<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/95.gif\" smileid=\"134\" alt=\"(bgm118)\"><br>所以想请教各位，这到底是什么奇怪的东西，它是盗版吗？ ","time":"2021-6-7 10:13","title":"买到一本奇怪的画集","userId":"yyfll","userName":"yyfll","userSign":"(本质KY，跳过别看)"}